This is the source code for the site and application CM Field Guide.

The purpose of this application is to detect what platform a website is running on.  The application is developed on the Django web application framework and works by running "signatures," Which Tests for varoius"tells" that are in little Python scripts of the site

If you know how to detect a particular CMS or web platform, we invite you to enhance or contribute a signature to improve the accuracy of the application.  Writing signatures is easy.  See the signatures package for examples.

Deane and Seth

